Interface NameableOrIdentifiable

    public interface NameableOrIdentifiable
extends Nameable, Identifiable
    Implements both Nameable and Identifiable interfaces
    In Java 8 we can avoid this type of interface that is needed for generics and replace with "<? extends Nameable & Identifiable>"
